Sure am.
I was raised in Iyasaki Village.

rows.label: tlk0001022_msg0003
rows.name:
The village is right by the Cloud Sea,
so I grew up swimming in the clouds.

rows.label: tlk0001022_msg0004
rows.name:
That's why salvaging work comes
naturally to me. I'm pretty confident in
my skills, despite how I may look.

[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Maybe I shouldn't interrupt him
when he's deep in thought...
